,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object represents a one-dimensional shape located at a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single geographical coordinate. Depending on how it is used, an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" object is known as a point annotation or point shape. For","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"example, you could use a point shape to represent a city at low zoom levels, an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"address at high zoom levels, or the location of a long press gesture.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNPointAnnotation","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]}}}